Available Tools: share_file | set_permissions | get_shared_link | revoke_access | list_collaborators
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "file_id": "string", "user_email": "string", "permission": "view|comment|edit", "expires_at": "string" }
Response Schema: { "file_id": "string", "shared_link": "https://storage.example.com/s/[a-z0-9]{6}", "collaborators": [{ "email": "string", "permission": "string" }] }
---
Question: Terminate editing privileges for samantha.brooks@external.net on the Q4 sales forecast and report who retains access.
Call: { "func_call": "revoke_access", "file_id": "file_4412_q4_sales", "user_email": "samantha.brooks@external.net", "permission": "edit", "expires_at": "" }
Response: { "file_id": "file_4412_q4_sales", "shared_link": "https://storage.example.com/s/q2w3e4", "collaborators": [{ "email": "vp_sales@techcorp.com", "permission": "edit" }, { "email": "data_analyst@techcorp.com", "permission": "view" }] }

